Here is a small program that examines the tar.Header structure for files starting with "root/" in the [fedora layer](https://registry-1.docker.io/v2/library/fedora/blobs/sha256:4db9daa7aafd1ea07f24d2ec893833adc17b5a9c5dde4150cf99a5789b3d322e) that is causing problems.  I don't see any Xattrs in anything.

https://gist.github.com/ae6rt/0100903271711499293d91ced0de998e

Run it:

```
tartool$ ./tartool sha256\:4db9daa7aafd1ea07f24d2ec893833adc17b5a9c5dde4150cf99a5789b3d322e.tar  
